playstore_details.title: স্বাস্থ্য কণিকা
playstore_details.description:
To decrease maternal and child mortality rate and a simply effort to achieved MDG goal. 
Health care is one of the basic needs of the people of Bangladesh. Every day we need to have numerous health information. Introductory information about the disease, What to do, Where to go, What can be done, What can not be, etc included in this app.
Maternal and Child health service and related upazila health complex mobile numbers for total emergency health service.
People of the world who uses Bengali language in Home and abroad through android user.
People get information about Antenatal, natal and post natal check-up, also get preventable child decreases and common child health problem, reproductive health, mental health,family planning, eyes, "Ear, Nose and Throat", Heart and lungs and also health awareness.
User can find trusted information when needed.
People of Bangladesh can get information about their health related problem by registered Doctor's through mobile numbers of upazila health complex by this app. 
All district and upazila health complex emergency mobile numbers are included here. This is Digital Health Service.
This app will minimize the necessity of being physically present at health service centers. Consequently, cost, time and number of visits will be minimized.
